<p><span style="font-size:75%;">This is a series showing off news from the site, articles from the past month<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup>, and fan-content for you to check out and discover! Be sure to leave a comment with your thoughts!</span></p>
<h4><span>Fandom Stuff</span></h4>
<ul>
<li>A new update has been published in the <a href="https://www.gofundme.com/f/scp-legal-funds">legal case</a> that many SCP fans have donated to support.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Recent updates to major browsers are making logging in to the wiki difficult for some people. A link has been added to the front page that <a href="/third-party-cookies">presents some solutions to the issue</a>.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://scp-int.wikidot.com/gruppi-di-interesse#SCEMC">The Most Serene College of Anomalies and Oddities of the Municipality</a>, a Group of Interest that has been gaining prominence in articles on SCP-IT (Italian language branch of the SCP Foundation) has been added to that branch's GoI hub page.</li>
</ul>
